  "text": "Root strength For analysis of root reinforced soil an estimate of the contribution of roots to stability is required (see 'stability modelling'). This may be obtained directly from in-situ root pull-out tests or from laboratory tests [CITATION_1] . Again account needs to be taken of the season at which the testing is completed compared with the most critical 'wet' periods for the site.",
